{"tid":1738050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢場運動而家先啱啱開始!!!!","createTime":"2019-11-19T06:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T07:03:18.000Z","uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"37fafcb427703f4f762ce2772beac179f481412a","tid":1738050,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:25:43.000Z","msg":"各位聽我講，對於營救行動失敗左大家都好唔開心，大家都不停放負，我哋過去一星期俾人帶風向，俾人揀咗戰場，不過其實我哋先係揀戰場嘅人，如果18區開花係救唔到人嘅話，咁我哋嘅目標就唔應該係救人，而係攻擊晒所有紅/黑，同埋繼續攻擊交通例如黨鐵。對家之所以為理大，目的就係為咗呃我哋嘅同情心，然後去送頭。為咗達到呢個目的佢唔會搞入邊嘅人着，即都係呢個時機我哋可以利用返理大人，聲東擊西"},{"pid":"16881e3102c56acac53c21f62a813a3eb85b0dc6","tid":1738050,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:26:52.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"513869b8ec321871e903c4fba542b6f178d8d9df","tid":1738050,"uid":293619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:26:57.000Z","msg":"有道理"},{"pid":"a2efb479d74221f161fb3e4421a2018b16610a17","tid":1738050,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:27:02.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"9b73c84691e02c9d4060a10a5b76042836988335","tid":1738050,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:27:12.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"965bd97062896b9376edd493de06ccabc30e278a","tid":1738050,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:27:22.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"d4b140545f58ff3a339c16b87ee7cfd3b13d647a","tid":1738050,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:27:32.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"12814b3702481f1237d8abc73b06ca298a3d06f1","tid":1738050,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:27:43.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"965ff722bd2b7ad8b16e1acf9b1b1d2bb271d3a8","tid":1738050,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"90f81cc1edf8f0d906a1eb2661060626bd08d1b3","tid":1738050,"uid":326261,